            },
            "body": "Hi, sorry for reply late.\r\n\r\nit seems all the improvements is depending on YARN-3409? the master branch do not support scheduling request yet.\r\n\r\nAnd for the 1st improvment, what i thought was add PC and allocataiontags on taskcontainer , but i read YARN-8007, and PC and\u00a0allocataiontags shouldn't add to container level.\r\n\r\nSo maybe we need create a new task class. PC,\u00a0allocataiontags and\u00a0taskcontainer are members of task class. What do you think?",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=Sichen+Zhao",
              "name": "Sichen Zhao",
              "key": "sichen zhao",
              "avatarUrls": {
